result.name: Olympian City 1

reviews.text: A modern residential complex with tennis courts and swimming pool located above the Olympic MTR station. There is a small shopping mall adjacent to it with some restaurants, supermarket and private clinics. Connected by a footbridge is Olympic City two and three which have bigger and more modern shopping malls.

This is the first phase of Olympian City. Compared to the newer phases across the highway, the selection of shops and restaurant is adequate and fairly easy to get used to quickly due to it's compact layout. It is not overly crowded either, making it a good regular shopping destination.
Only decent shops here are JHC, 7-Eleven and Marketplace.
Huge shopping centre packed with stores. Pleasant experience with good amenities.
The place that you can relax ,eat and see the view of the sea
